TEXT.TITLE: AMERIBANC <AINV.O>, CARDINAL END ACQUISITION
TEXT.BODY: Ameribanc Investors Group and Cardinal Savings and Loan Association jointly announced that the proposed acquisition of Cardinal by Ameribanc has been terminated by mutual agreement. Reuter
